## ACU Lifecycle

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> New: createACU()
    New --> Active: state = 'ACTIVE'
    Active --> Updated: updateImportance()
    Active --> Archived: archive()
    Active --> Deleted: delete()
    Updated --> Active
    Archived --> Active: restore()
    Archived --> Deleted: permanent delete
    Deleted --> [*]

    note right of New: Just extracted<br/>from message
    note right of Active: Available for<br/>retrieval
    note right of Updated: Importance changed<br/>by decay model
    note right of Archived: Soft-deleted<br/>still queryable
    note right of Deleted: Hard delete<br/>permanent removal
```

